      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing and driving exactly as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with no scratches or swirls, and the interior remains pristine with no signs of wear. Every mechanical and electronic component functions perfectly, and the car has been meticulously garage-kept and professionally maintained. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that is essentially brand new in every way.",
