      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "We are privileged to offer this exemplary motorcar, maintained to a standard that defies its age. This vehicle presents in showroom condition, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains entirely unblemished. Every component has been meticulously vetted to ensure peak performance, offering a rare opportunity for the sophisticated buyer to acquire a specimen of unparalleled pedigree.",
