      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I am beyond excited to show you this absolute beauty. It has been my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it\u2019s in such pristine, mint condition that you\u2019d think it just rolled off the showroom floor today! It\u2019s been pampered and kept spotless inside and out. I\u2019m still building up my seller rating here, so I\u2019m offering this gem at a fantastic price to get things moving. You won't find a smoother, cleaner ride\u2014come see it for yourself and let's get you behind the wheel! \u2728",
