      "description": "An exceptional specimen of the E46 M3, this vehicle features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Double-VANOS system, both fully serviced for optimal valve timing. Power is channeled through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to the rear wheels via a variable M differential lock. The chassis is structurally flawless, including a reinforced rear subframe and a suspension setup that retains its factory-spec damping and lateral stiffness. With linear power delivery and a razor-sharp throttle response, this car represents a rare opportunity for a collector seeking mechanical perfection.",
